Greg invites them to his family's&nbsp;
lakehouse to get away. While Jay sleeps,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:06:16.400 --> 00:06:19.840
Paul watches over her, considering Jeff's&nbsp;
suggestion of Jay passing the curse.

00:06:20.800 --> 00:06:24.720
The following day, Greg teaches Jay how&nbsp;
to use a revolver to protect herself.

00:06:25.520 --> 00:06:30.480
While hanging out by the shore with Paul, Kelly,&nbsp;
