00:10:10.800 --> 00:10:15.280
estimating its position. He finally shoots&nbsp;
it on the head again, and Jay is free.

00:10:15.280 --> 00:10:16.880
Kelly helps Jay get out of the pool.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:10:17.440 --> 00:10:22.080
